===Gem rates===
When a gem rock is mined, one of the following [[gems]] is produced:
{{DropsTableHead}}
{{DropsLineReward|name=Uncut opal|quantity=1|rarity=60/128}}
{{DropsLineReward|name=Uncut jade|quantity=1|rarity=30/128}}
{{DropsLineReward|name=Uncut red topaz|quantity=1|rarity=15/128}}
{{DropsLineReward|name=Uncut sapphire|quantity=1|rarity=9/128}}
{{DropsLineReward|name=Uncut emerald|quantity=1|rarity=5/128}}
{{DropsLineReward|name=Uncut ruby|quantity=1|rarity=5/128}}
{{DropsLineReward|name=Uncut diamond|quantity=1|rarity=4/128}}
{{DropsTableBottom}}

Taking this into consideration, mining a gem rock is worth {{Coins|{{Average drop value|mob=Gem rock|raw=y}}}} on average. 

